title: Assorted Knifemaking Books
description:
This is from another request, but I wanted to upload this eventually anyway.  Various knifemaking and sharpening books are contained.

Includes:
-The Modern Blacksmith- Alexander G. Weygers
-The Razor Edge Book of Knife Sharpening- John Juranitch
-The Complete Bladesmith- Forging Your Way to Perfection- Jim Hrisoulas
-Step-by-Step Knifemaking- David Boye
-Everybody's Knife Bible- Don Paul
-And much more.

~~~
